nodes.text: Ulda was the first wife of Kitster Chanchani Banai, who had left her for an employee of Ulda's, Tamora Spice. Ulda owned and maintained the old Mos Espa Grand Arena in 8.5 ABY, in time to help Han and Leia Organa Solo in their search for the painting Killik Twilight, supplying them with a swoop bike to chase down her ex-husband.
